Kraken offer solutions that are comparable to its competitors. Karken top advantage its is security ratings. “ Since its inception Kraken has been committed to building a crypto platform with the highest standards for security, performance and reliability.” (blog.Kraken.com
In the digital world of trading that is one of the most valuable assets. It also supports most countries, in comparison with its counterparts. This is one of their key competitive advantages. 

Additionally, “Kraken is the only exchange that offer access to Monero” (Financebuzz.com). “If you’re more interested in altcoins, Kraken has the most value”. Kraken also “offers a wide variety of order types, as well as access to margin”. (Financebuzz.com)


